  "Low variability relative to the mean": "",
  "A standard deviation of 5": "",
  "A mean of 5": "",
  "Very high variability relative to the mean": "",
  "A CV of 5% means the standard deviation is only 5% of the mean, indicating relatively low spread.": "",
